From bdeba1e73084af81909e281aa706696ac04e5565 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Sep 2024 04:20:33 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 63/78] Platform/Sgi: Create voyager-r1 platform specific dsc
 files

There are currently two voyager-r1 platforms that are supported under
SgiPkg and these platforms have a common platform dsc file to allow these
to be built into a single binary. But the newer platforms that are
intended to be added to the SgiPkg differ to some extent on the software
programming interface. So in order to accommodate the newer platforms
into SgiPkg, there is shift from building single binary for all
platforms to independent binary for each platform.

As a first step towards this, create .dsc file for each supported
platform. The exiting .dsc file is converted to be a include file
that the platform specific .dsc files can include

Signed-off-by: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Change-Id: Ie4ab231bb4910c3fdc98af1760356a7b7a57de6e
---
 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatform4.dsc.inc | 36 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 36 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatform4.dsc.inc

diff --git a/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatform4.dsc.inc b/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatform4.dsc.inc
new file mode 100644
index 000000000000..91c3855d1a54
--- /dev/null
+++ b/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatform4.dsc.inc
@@ -0,0 +1,36 @@
